title: Video courses from Teamtreehouse
description:
I activated 2-week trial and want to share some lessons from teamtreehouse.com.
There is few themes highlited:
-web-design (basics and instruments)
-front-end web-development (css tricks, a lot of javaScript guides etc.)
-working with MySQL databases
-Development for CMS Wordpress

Video files can't give full image without tests and code challenges from original site, so, if you want to became real professional or have questions - activate your own trial or purchase subscriptions. Guys from teamtreehouse deserve this
